About:
_

A showcase collection of nearly 200 outstanding sample resumes and 12 cover letters representing the very best creations of professional resume writers.

About the Author
__

Hundreds of thousands of people know David F. Noble, Ph.D., as the author of the resume book that helped them find jobs. His many best-selling books include Gallery of Best Resumes and Gallery of Best Cover Letters. He has more than 20 years of experience teaching English, writing, American Literature, business editing at several universities. 

He currently teaches English at the University of Indianapolis. He is frequently call on by professional resume writers' associations to write and present on the mechanics of resume writing.
